definitions.definition: A misshapen person; a misshapen body .
A misshapen object; now especially, a broken item (especially food) sold individually at a cheaper price.

main_definition: ( obsolete ) A misshapen person; a misshapen body . [14th–17th c.]
secondary_definitions: A misshapen object; now especially, a broken item (especially food) sold individually at a cheaper price. [from 19th c.]
